NarrPara.Content: Before we can define bag displays, we require the definition of $items$, which appears later. For the same reason, the laws about displays also appear later.

\subsection{Bag displays}
Now that we have defined $items$, we can define bag displays in terms of it, as mentioned by Spivey at the beginning of Section 4.6 of his book.
An example of usage of bag displays for empty and singleton bags
